All Implemented Interfaces:
IDeployAttributeValidator
public class CapabilityAttributeUniqueInGroupValidator
extends DeployAttributeValidator

Validates that the attribute of a Capability is unique in the group of its Unit.

Example: assert that v1 != v2 

 +------------------+    +------------------+
 | Cap1: Capability |    | Cap2: Capability |
 +------------------+    +------------------+
 | attribute a = v1 |    | attribute a = v2 |
 +------------------+    +------------------+
       ˆ                           ˆ
       | Capabilities              | Capabilities
 +------------------+    +------------------+
 | Container1: Unit |    | Container2: Unit |
 +------------------+    +------------------+
       ˆ                              ˆ
       | MemberLink                   | MemberLink
 +------------------+                 |
 | Group: Unit      |-----------------+
 +------------------+
